These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, r&b
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, gardening
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | trance |
| Hobby         | gardening | woodworking    |
| Beverage     | fanta     | milk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, crime
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, sailing
House: cottage, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Movie-Genre      | crime  | spy   |
| Sport   | sailing | skateboarding  |
| House     | futuristic   | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, january
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
1. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Pet         | goat   | goldfish  |
| Birthday   | january | november  |
| Beverage         | almond-milk   | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
City: edinburgh, prague
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, journalist
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, mauve
1. the person who likes red is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| City          | edinburgh | prague |
| Job   | journalist   | architect   |
| Color     | mauve       | red      |

