.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, disaster
2 different pets are kept: horse, rat
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
3. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Movie-Genre    | disaster | scientific     |
| Pet     | rat | horse |
| Hobby   | hiking | photography    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-8::.
