2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | monopoly       |
| Transport      | bike     | scooter  |
| Cigar        | bongani          | bolivar |

